Generate a sanitized diagnostic bundle

Usage: mxr bug-report [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --edit             
      --stdout           
      --clipboard        
      --github           
      --output <OUTPUT>  
      --verbose          
      --full-logs        
      --no-sanitize      
      --since <SINCE>    
